animeDescription: Rat, a member of the Zodiac, meets a normal cat at a park one day. Rat comes to love Cat so much that it becomes very eager to get Cat to become a member of the Zodiac. Cat goes with Rat to meet the rest of the 12 members of the Zodiac to ask them to become a member.  (Source: ANN)
animeVoices: ['Kugimiya, Rie', 'Masuda, Yuki', 'Shingaki, Tarusuke', 'Cho', 'Yonaga, Tsubasa', 'Tomatsu, Haruka', 'Ookawa, Tooru']
